OL,7,FThe Criminal Injuries Compensation
OL,8,FAuthority (CICA) was criticised for
OL,9,Frising waiting times for victims to
OL,10,Fget a decision over whether they would
OL,11,Fget compensation, with nearly a fifth
OL,12,Fof claimants waiting more than two
OL,13,Fyears for an answer according to its
OL,14,Flatest annual report. Some have to
OL,15,Fwait more than five years for a
OL,16,Fverdict.
