OL,7,FMeanwhile, more than a third of
OL,8,Fdecisions by the body that had been
OL,9,Fappealed were successfully overturned.
OL,10,FThe number of complaints has more than
OL,11,Fdoubled in a year.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice has blamed
OL,14,Fthis on a record number of
OL,15,Fapplications. A spokesperson said it
OL,16,Fwas hiring more staff and attempting
OL,17,Fto improve its communications.
