OL,4,Ccompensation scheme amid claims it
OL,5,Cadds to trauma
OL,7,FConcerns have led a dozen Labour MPs,
OL,8,Fled by Laurence Turner (Birmingham
OL,9,FNorthfield) to support a Private
OL,10,FMember's Bill that would launch a
OL,11,F"fundamental" review of the scheme.
OL,13,FBaroness Newlove, the late Victims'
OL,14,FCommissioner criticised it before her
OL,15,Fdeath in November, as the Government
OL,16,Fdeclined to alter the scheme five
OL,17,Fyears after it began a consultation on
OL,18,Fchanges.
