OL,7,FNatalie Queiroz applied to the
OL,8,Fcompensation authority after her
OL,9,Fpartner attempted to kill her and her
OL,10,Funborn baby in Sutton Coldfield in
OL,11,F2016.
OL,13,FMs Queiroz, now 49, was stabbed 24
OL,14,Ftimes in a nine-minute attack while
OL,15,Fshe was eight months pregnant. She and
OL,16,Fher daughter received lifesaving
OL,17,Ftreatment ` with her applying to CICA
OL,18,Ffor them both afterwards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
