OL,7,FShe criticised its "horrendously
OL,8,Fcomplex process" and the need to rank
OL,9,Fyour own injuries. She has since had
OL,10,Fto have her finger amputated, and
OL,11,Fcertain injuries have since worsened
OL,12,Fin the nine years after the attack.
OL,14,FMs Querioz said: "I incurred
OL,15,Fsignificant traumatic injuries in my
OL,16,Fchest which led to me taking nerve
OL,17,Fblockers initially to cope with the
OL,18,Fpain.
