OL,7,F"When the knife went through my
OL,8,Fribcage it caused significant nerve
OL,9,Fand cartilage damage between my ribs
OL,10,Fwhich led to horrendous pain, as well
OL,11,Fas leave significant scarring in my
OL,12,Flungs from the stabbing.
OL,14,F"Nobody knew how my lungs would
OL,15,Frecover and unfortunately I've had
OL,16,Fpneumonia four times since then due to
OL,17,Fmy lungs being unable to clear any
OL,18,Fchest infections.
