OL,7,F"So, you end up in this situation of
OL,8,Fhow do I rank them? Then there's often
OL,9,Fpsychological elements, I'm literally
OL,10,Fwriting out all my injuries, but you
OL,11,Fhave to pick your top three."
OL,13,FShe added: "You have a time limit of
OL,14,Fhow long it is you can apply, so
OL,15,Fyou're in this kind of horrible
OL,16,Fsituation where you are recovering
OL,17,Ffrom physical and emotional trauma,
OL,18,Fyou've got this complex form, and
OL,19,Fyou're thinking 'I don't know what the
OL,20,Fextent of these injuries will be.'"
