OL,7,FMs Queiroz has since been appointed
OL,8,Fvictims commissioner for West
OL,9,FMidlands, where she has spoken to
OL,10,Fothers who have applied to CICA. She
OL,11,Fwas awarded an MBE in Queen Elizabeth
OL,12,FII's final birthday honours in 2022
OL,13,Ffor services to young people and the
OL,14,Fprevention of knife crime.
OL,16,FShe said: "People just find it really
OL,17,Fconfusing, really quite scary, don't
OL,18,Freally understand it, some people call
OL,19,Fit like a dark art of how you write
OL,20,Fout the forms to get compensation."
