OL,7,FMr Turner, who applied to CICA after a
OL,8,Fviolent assault before the Covid
OL,9,Fpandemic led to four operations, told
OL,10,Fthe Press Association: "It was a
OL,11,Ftypical experience that many victims
OL,12,Freport; impersonal contact, very long
OL,13,Fdelays in getting the case resolved,
OL,14,Fand the outcome never felt like
OL,15,Fadequate recompense for the nature of
OL,16,Finjuries."
