OL,7,FHe had to wait almost two years to get
OL,8,Fhis case resolved and said: "By the
OL,9,Ftime you get to the end of that
OL,10,Fexhausting process where you've had to
OL,11,Frepeat and relive some really quite
OL,12,Ftraumatic experiences, lots of victims
OL,13,Fjust want the process to be over."
OL,15,FMr Turner added: "I always knew I
OL,16,Fwanted to try and do something about
OL,17,Fit because when you've had a very
OL,18,Fnegative experience, you want some
OL,19,Fgood to come out of it."
