OL,3,CCalls for overhaul of victims'
OL,4,Ccompensation scheme amid claims it
OL,5,Cadds to trauma
OL,7,FThe scheme was set up in the 1960s to
OL,8,Fprovide compensation to the victims of
OL,9,Fviolent crime. However it has been
OL,10,Fcriticised, including by the late
OL,11,FVictims Commissioner Baroness Newlove,
OL,12,Fwho reported in 2019 that the system
OL,13,Fwas adding to victims' upset,
OL,14,Fincluding with an overly complex
OL,15,Fapplication process and long waits for
OL,16,Fdecisions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
