OL,3,CCalls for overhaul of victims'
OL,4,Ccompensation scheme amid claims it
OL,5,Cadds to trauma
OL,7,FThe Government commissioned a
OL,8,Fconsultation to find how the scheme
OL,9,Fcould be made simpler. Yet after an
OL,10,Falmost five-year wait, Justice
OL,11,FMinister Alex Davies-Jones said she
OL,12,Fwould not be taking on recommendations
OL,13,Fof the inquiry.
OL,15,FMs Davies-Jones said changes to time
OL,16,Flimits and unspent convictions that
OL,17,Fcould benefit the victims of child
OL,18,Fsexual abuse could "be detrimental to
OL,19,Fother deserving victims of crime".
