OL,3,CCalls for overhaul of victims'
OL,4,Ccompensation scheme amid claims it
OL,5,Cadds to trauma
OL,7,FThe decision was criticised by
OL,8,FBaroness Newlove, who died in November.
OL,10,FAlex Mayes, external affairs manager
OL,11,Fat Victim Support urged the need for
OL,12,Ffundamental changes.
OL,14,FMr Mayes said: "We definitely need to
OL,15,Fbe in a place where CICA are
OL,16,Fprocessing claims at pace, where
OL,17,Fthere's not a substantial backlog,
OL,18,Fwhere victims aren't having to wait
OL,19,Flong periods of time to get outcomes
OL,20,Fand to have their claims dealt with.
OL,26,@vD@POU
