OL,3,CCalls for overhaul of victims'
OL,4,Ccompensation scheme amid claims it
OL,5,Cadds to trauma
OL,7,F"While they're waiting, victims need
OL,8,Fto be treated with sensitivity,
OL,9,Fcompassion, respect, and we need to
OL,10,Fhave a victim-first approach to
OL,11,Fcompensation claims and victims don't
OL,12,Fneed to be in a position where they're
OL,13,Fwaiting years and years and years for
OL,14,Fan outcome."
OL,16,FLabour MP Alex Sobel (Leeds Central
OL,17,Fand Headingly) said he had two
OL,18,Fconstituents who had put claims
OL,19,Fforward, including someone who had to
OL,20,Fwait six years for an outcome.
