OL,7,FMr Sobel said medical evidence which
OL,8,Fhad been sent in to support claims had
OL,9,Fbeen lost by CICA, and people were
OL,10,Fleft feeling ignored by slow response
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,13,FHe said: "We want them basically to
OL,14,Fimprove their performance, timescales,
OL,15,Fdelivery, communication, and the
OL,16,Frealism of it."
